attributes.Long form description: The general instruction is to disassemble the furniture. The student starts by unscrewing the top hex socket heads to remove the top table. After that the student unscrews the hex socket heads from the shelf, by doing this, he is able to remove the legs one by one and leave all parts on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Well, now disassemble the shelf from IKEA. So please go ahead and disassemble.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the top table.
The student disassembles the first leg.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student dropped the hex socket head by accident.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the second leg.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student dropped the hex socket head by accident.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the third leg.
The student disassembles the rest of the table including the fourth leg and the lower tray.
